channel.title: Vivian Wong
channel.description: Hi! I am a graduate student at Stanford University studying Civil Engineering. My interests are in solving critical societal and urban problems with the help of computational methods such as digital simulation and AI.

item.title: My Personal Site
item.description: I am building this website so that there could be one day when you look up “Vivian Wong” in a search engine looking for my information you would not find yourself more knowledgeable in Yu-Gi-Oh! This is what appears 1st place in Google right now if you look up my name.
